    Represents an action over the state space of the MDP
    MDP.Feature
    Represents a feature (real valued function over the state space of the MDP)
    MDP.FiniteSFeature
    Class representing a feature for a finite state space MDP - it provides functionality to have binary features (activated to 1 over a subset, and 0 everywhere else)
